Company Overview of Employees Retirement System of Texas



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Employees Retirement System of Texas (ERS) is a public pension fund with $21 billion in assets under management. ERS administers programs that provide retirement, health insurance, deferred compensation, and flexible benefits for retirees and current state employees and their dependents. The fund is headquartered in Austin, Texas.


200 East 18th StreetAustin, TX 78701United States



Phone: 512-867-7711

Fax: 512-867-7438

www.ers.state.tx.us







