Home > Retirees > Health > Overview
Overview









BenefitsERS offers a variety of medical and optional benefits to retirees and their families. Health BenefitsLearn how ERS can help take care of you and qualified dependents.  Optional BenefitsMore information about our basic life insurance and disability benefits.  How Medicare WorksFind out how and when to enroll in Medicare.  Change Your Benefits    Once per year, you have the option to change your benefits choices. Qualifying life events, like marriage, children, moving, and more, allow you to make benefits changes during the plan year. See all qualifying life events >ERS RetirementResources after retirement: Your ERS Connection Retiree Newsletter Subscribe to stay informed on what's new and important. Online Account Services Manage your retirement account and benefits through your online account.         




















